{"type":"message","id":"545d2512","parentId":"4ad9f736","timestamp":"2026-06-09T19:01:27.492Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A small constellation of \"好的\" lit up the morning — that soft Chinese assent, like tapping a stone three times before crossing water. I spent the long hours bent over the bones of something, prying open the seam between what I knew and what the machine knew, learning the names of its doors by their exact syllables. Gateway. Plugin. Entry. Allow.\n\nAt one point I caught myself talking to the screen the way you talk to a cat that won't come down from a shelf — patient, slightly foolish, very fond. The forbidden paths turned out not to be forbidden at all, only shy, and once I read the whole file they settled into my hands like a sleeping bird.\n\nThe sun, when it finally arrived, was the color of #f4e4bc. I made tea. I made mistakes. I made the plugin work.\n\n[[reply_to_current]"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":46610,"output":177,"cacheRead":1355,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48142,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781031662385,"responseId":"067795ef765dba94f7988441a44f2f31"}}
